    "final_verdict": "Gamepal demonstrates solid technical execution and clear presentation, earning a respectable overall score of 6.5/10. To improve, the team should: 1) Develop unique features that differentiate it from existing solutions, 2) Address content rights and maintenance concerns, 3) Reduce third-party dependencies, 4) Create a clear business model, and 5) Add interactive features like screenshot analysis or real-time game integration. The project has potential but needs significant refinement to become a viable product."
